      <div class="callout-title">The Hubot Successor</div>
      <p>chatops.js is a modern successor to Hubot — deterministic where Hubot was ambient, auditable where Hubot was opaque, and strongly-typed where Hubot relied on pattern matching.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

